            <note xml:id="foot.f4">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-12711.xml">letter to Adolf Ernst, 11 September 1880</ref> and n. 1.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f5">The <hi rend="italic">American Naturalist</hi> was edited by <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_3639.xml">Alpheus Spring Packard</ref> and <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1066.xml">Edward Drinker Cope</ref>; no correction by Ernst appears to have been published.</note>
